<body>

    <%- include('partials/header.ejs'); %>

    <!-- Start banner Area -->
    <section class="banner-area" id="home" style="position: relative; background-image: url('/images/about.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat; height: 600px;">
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); z-index: 1;"></div> <!-- Dark overlay -->
        <div class="container" style="position: relative; z-index: 2;">
            <div class="row fullscreen d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="height: 100%;">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <div class="banner-content text-white" style="width: 80%; margin: auto;">
                        <h1 class="banner-title" style="font-size: 3rem; margin: 0; color: #fff;">About Us</h1>
                        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #ddd; margin-top: 10px;">
                            Learn more about our journey, mission, and the passionate team behind our book review platform. We are committed to providing insightful reviews and fostering a community of avid readers.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- End banner Area -->

    <!-- Start About Section -->
    <section class="about" style="padding: 60px 0; background-color: #f9f9f9;">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center" style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #333;">About Literary Realm</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                Welcome to Literary Realm, your ultimate destination for discovering and exploring the world of books. Our platform is designed for book enthusiasts to find, review, and share their favorite reads.
            </p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 40px; color: #333;">Our Mission</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                At Literary Realm, our mission is to create a vibrant community of readers who can connect over their shared love of books. We aim to provide a seamless experience for users to discover new books, rate and review them, and maintain their personal reading lists.
            </p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 40px; color: #333;">Features</h3>
            <ul style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <li>Comprehensive book database with detailed information.</li>
                <li>Sort functionality to easily find books.</li>
                <li>User ratings and reviews to help you choose your next read.</li>
                <li>Personalized book lists and recommendations.</li>
                <li>Integration with Open Library API for up-to-date book information.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 40px; color: #333;">Meet the Team</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                Our team is composed of passionate book lovers and tech enthusiasts dedicated to enhancing your reading experience. We are constantly working to improve the platform and add new features based on user feedback.
            </p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 40px; color: #333;">Contact Us</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                If you have any questions, suggestions, or feedback, feel free to reach out to us through our <a href="/contact" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;">Contact</a> page. We'd love to hear from you!
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- End About Section -->

